OL,3,CWhich delivery companies are the best
OL,4,C(and worst) for customer satisfaction?
OL,6,FWhen comparing firms' performances in
OL,7,Fhandling queries, Amazon and FedEx
OL,8,Ftopped the poll on customer service
OL,9,Fsatisfaction, both achieving a score
OL,10,Fof 57%.
OL,12,FThey were closely followed by UPS and
OL,13,FDHL, both at 55%.
OL,15,FYodel and Evri, at the bottom of the
OL,16,Franking, only managed scores of 38%
OL,17,Fand 31% respectively.
OL,19,FBoth firms also had the highest levels
OL,20,Fof dissatisfaction, with Evri scoring
OL,21,F41% and Yodel 33%.
